 2016-04132016-05-20,  ,  ,  ,  PSPC, 
ActFinancial Administration Act
SubjectCanada Lands Company Ltd. ** Corporate Plan **
PrecisOrder (1) approving the CORPORATE PLAN of the CANADA LANDS COMPANY LIMITED for the 2016-17 to 2020-21 planning period; (2) authorizing the OLD PORT OF MONTRÉAL CORPORATION INC. to enter into up to 100 leases in 2016-17; (3) authorizing PARC DOWNSVIEW PARK INC. to enter into up to 60 leases in 2016-17; and (4) approving that CANADA LANDS COMPANY LIMITED return a reduced dividend in 2016-17 and no dividend in 2017-18.
